    "description_long": "This is a modern hatchback car with a vibrant red exterior and a contrasting black roof, featuring a panoramic glass sunroof. The vehicle has sleek, aerodynamic lines, chrome accents along the windows and lower body, and a prominent front grille with a mesh pattern. The headlights are sharply contoured, and the taillights have a distinctive vertical design. The car is equipped with five-spoke alloy wheels and side mirrors with integrated turn signals. The interior, visible through the windows, appears to have a spacious cabin with multiple seating rows and a dashboard typical of contemporary hatchbacks.",
